  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They'd asked me to do it, and I did it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They sent him things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They sent  him clothes, which he probably didn't need.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they sent money when-- some of the families he stayed with demanded money, so they sent money.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But later, in the '80s, after my father died, my mother went one more time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We took her on one of our yearly trips.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so she only saw him-- between '46 and the rest of her life, she only saw him two more times.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I stayed in Toronto until I married my present husband, which, which was really a very fortunate thing, not only because I was only 46 when I lost my husband-- I was still a young woman-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] but because my parents lived in Bridgeport.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I was able to help them, you know, as they got older and, and, and their health was no longer as good.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I always liked-- even though our, our personal relationship was not of the-- you know, it was not of the best quality, you might put it that way, I always felt very keenly-- I was always very anxious that they be well taken care of.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was much easier to do it from here than from Toronto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father was a very sickly person, but my mother took care of him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was very strong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But in, in the last couple of years, she herself got very sick.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I was very glad that I was here and was able to look after her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now you are devoting yourself to, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to recalling and to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] bringing out so much of your experiences.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
